videos.headline: Walker returns punt to the house
videos.description: Boston College WR Michael Walker fields the punt after it hits a Clemson player and returns it 74 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Lawence lobs perfect TD pass to Richard
videos.description: On 4th-and-goal, Clemson QB Trevor Lawrence lobs a pass just over a defender's hands and into TE Milan Richard's for the touchdown.

videos.headline: Brown leaves game after taking hard hit
videos.description: Boston College QB Anthony Brown takes a hard hit after throwing an incomplete pass in the first quarter. Brown would head to the locker room.

videos.headline: Boston College recovers controversial muffed punt
videos.description: Taj-Amir Torres appears to run into Amari Rodgers before the ball gets there, causing a fumble and Torres recovers for the Eagles with no flag.

videos.headline: Clemson on top of Boston College at the half
videos.description: The Clemson Tigers hold a 13-7 lead over Boston College behind Trevor Lawrence's 211 yards passing and one touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Clemson on top of Boston College at the half) 2018/11/10 ESHEET SotFull

videos.headline: Lawrence waltzes in for TD on keeper
videos.description: Trevor Lawrence fakes a handoff and speeds into the end zone for the score to extend Clemson's lead over Boston College.

videos.headline: Rodgers evades tacklers on punt return TD
videos.description: Clemson WR Amari Rodgers fields the punt, speeds away from multiple Boston College players and returns it 58 yards for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Dabo 'thankful' to clinch another division title
videos.description: Clemson head coach Dabo Swinney reacts to clinching the ACC Atlantic division on the 10th anniverary of his first win with the Tigers.
